Document: OpenXRSpatialEntityTracker
Path: godot/classes/class_openxrspatialentitytracker.rst
Summary: This class represents trackers created by OpenXR's spatial entity extensions that provide access to OpenXR spatial entity data.

These are trackers created and managed by OpenXR's spatial entity extensions that give access to specific data related to OpenXR's spatial entities. They will always be of type TRACKER_ANCHOR.
