Document: OpenXRSpatialEntityTracker
Path: godot/classes/class_openxrspatialentitytracker.rst
Summary: Properties and their default values for the OpenXRSpatialEntityTracker class.

- RID (RID): Unique resource identifier. Default: RID()
- EntityTrackingState (EntityTrackingState): Current tracking state of the entity. Default: 2
- TrackerType (TrackerType): Type of tracker device. Default: 8 (overrides XRTracker's type property)
Note: The TrackerType value 8 overrides the default type value from the XRTracker class.
