Document: OpenXRSpatialEntityTracker  
Path: godot/classes/class_openxrspatialentitytracker.rst  
Summary: Describes the entity association and spatial tracking state properties for the OpenXR spatial entity tracker class.  

entity (RID): The spatial entity associated with this tracker. Default: RID(). Set via set_entity(value: RID), retrieved via get_entity() → RID.  

spatial_tracking_state (EntityTrackingState): The spatial tracking state for this tracker. Default: 2. Set via set_spatial_tracking_state(value: EntityTrackingState), retrieved via get_spatial_tracking_state() → EntityTrackingState.